title: BRIEF-Audioeye Reports First Quarter, Revenue Increases 153% To $1.1 Mln, Bookings Accelerate To $2.2 Million
text:
04 AM / Updated 8 minutes ago BRIEF-Audioeye Reports First Quarter, Revenue Increases 153% To $1.1 Mln, Bookings Accelerate To $2.2 Million Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 17 (Reuters) - AudioEye Inc: 
* AUDIOEYE REPORTS RECORD FIRST QUARTER, REVENUE INCREASES 153% TO $1.1 MILLION, BOOKINGS ACCELERATE TO $2.2 MILLION 
* SEES FY 2018 REVENUE $6.5 MILLION TO $7.5 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
